>
> **Output:** A single self-contained HTML snippet with all CSS in a `<style>` block and all JS in a `<script>` block. No external dependencies beyond the fonts `DM Sans` and `Fraunces` (already loaded by the app). The entire snippet drops directly into the app's `.app-main` layout area.

